# Deployment Configuration Rules

## Azure Configuration Values
Always use these exact values when providing deployment commands:

- **Resource Group**: `hustlemode.ai`
- **App Service Name**: `hustlemode`
- **App Service Plan**: `hustlemode-plan`
- **Location**: `eastus`
- **Runtime**: `PYTHON:3.11`
- **SKU**: `B1`

## Command Templates

### Azure App Service Commands
```bash
# Create App Service Plan
az appservice plan create --name hustlemode-plan --resource-group hustlemode.ai --sku B1 --location eastus

# Create Web App
az webapp create --name hustlemode --resource-group hustlemode.ai --plan hustlemode-plan --runtime "PYTHON:3.11"

# Configure Environment Variables
az webapp config appsettings set --name hustlemode --resource-group hustlemode.ai --settings @.env

# Set up Local Git Deployment
az webapp deployment source config-local-git --name hustlemode --resource-group hustlemode.ai

# Restart App Service
az webapp restart --name hustlemode --resource-group hustlemode.ai

# View Logs
az webapp log tail --name hustlemode --resource-group hustlemode.ai
```

### Database Commands
```bash
# Create PostgreSQL Server
az postgres flexible-server create --name hustlemode-db --resource-group hustlemode.ai --location eastus --admin-user postgres --admin-password <password> --sku-name Standard_B1ms --storage-size 32

# Create Database
az postgres flexible-server db create --resource-group hustlemode.ai --server-name hustlemode-db --database-name hustlemode
```

